  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Allyrion\" title=\"House Allyrion\"><img alt=\"House Allyrion.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Allyrion.svg/50px-House_Allyrion.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Allyrion.svg/75px-House_Allyrion.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/House_Allyrion.svg/100px-House_Allyrion.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Ryon Allyrion</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Allyrion\" title=\"House Allyrion\"><img alt=\"House Allyrion.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Allyrion.svg/50px-House_Allyrion.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Allyrion.svg/75px-House_Allyrion.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/House_Allyrion.svg/100px-House_Allyrion.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Allyrion\" title=\"House Allyrion\">House Allyrion</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nor before <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_264_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">264&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Delonne_Allyrion\" title=\"Delonne Allyrion\">Delonne Allyrion</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ynys_Yronwood\" title=\"Ynys Yronwood\">Ynys Yronwood</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Sand\" title=\"Daemon Sand\">Daemon Sand</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li>Two trueborn sons<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Ryon Allyrion</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Allyrion\" title=\"House Allyrion\">House Allyrion</a>. He is the son and heir of <a href=\"/index.php/Delonne_Allyrion\" title=\"Delonne Allyrion\">Delonne Allyrion</a>, Lady of <a href=\"/index.php/Godsgrace\" title=\"Godsgrace\">Godsgrace</a>. Ryon is married to <a href=\"/index.php/Ynys_Yronwood\" title=\"Ynys Yronwood\">Ynys Yronwood</a>, with whom he has children, at least two sons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> He also has a <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> son, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Sand\" title=\"Daemon Sand\">Daemon Sand</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ryon_Allyrion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ryon_Allyrion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser Ryon is among the group of nobles that accompanies Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> for the wedding of King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ryon_Allyrion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ryon is present in <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>, along with his bastard son, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Sand\" title=\"Daemon Sand\">Daemon Sand</a>, at the feast when Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Swann\" title=\"Balon Swann\">Balon Swann</a> arrives in <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a> to deliver the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountain%27s_skull\" title=\"Mountain&#39;s skull\">Mountain's skull</a>. He drinks when <a href=\"/index.php/Ricasso\" title=\"Ricasso\">Ricasso</a> raises a toast to King <a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen I Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ryon_Allyrion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Delonne_Allyrion\" title=\"Delonne Allyrion\">Delonne</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />husband</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\